      "description": "The TSPY Lift ETF (TSYX) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in large cap equity. The fund is actively managed, seeking to provide 1.3x leveraged exposure to the daily price movement of TappAlpha SPY Growth & Daily Income ETF (ticker: TSPY) through total return swap agreements. The reference ETF holds long exposure to the S&P 500 Index and writes daily out-of-the-money calls, using 0DTE options. TSYX was launched on Jan 7, 2026 and is issued by TappAlpha.",
